 the days are coming” —this is the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s declaration —“when I will restore the fortunes "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or will end the captivity"},{"kind":"text","text":" of my people Israel and Judah,” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 33:7","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 33:11","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 37:15–23","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 39:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":39,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 3:1","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 9:14","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" says the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":". “I will restore them to the land I gave to their ancestors and they will possess it.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 33:7","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":7},{"label":"Jr 33:11","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":11},{"label":"Ezk 37:15–23","book":"Ezk","chapter":37,"verse":15},{"label":"Ezk 39:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":39,"verse":25},{"label":"Jl 3:1","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Am 9:14","book":"Amo","chapter":9,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or will end the captivity"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:30:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are the words the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" spoke to Israel and Judah. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:30:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says:"},{"kind":"text","text":" We have heard a cry of terror,"},{"kind":"text","text":" of dread —there is no peace."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a